        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7258",
        "content": "Is it not the worst of sacrilege, a foul profanation of our human nature, which for us, at least, should be holy and awful, when the heroic and saintly martyrdom of a true Man is thus falsified into the self schemed sham sacrifice, ineffectual, of a God?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
