        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7258",
        "content": "He is the good Pan, the great Shepherd.... at whose death were moanings, sighs, trepidations and lamentations in all the machine of the universe, heavens, earth, sea, hells.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
